companyName: ETRACS Monthly Pay 2xLeveraged S&P Dividend ETN
description:
The investment seeks to replicate, net of expenses, the monthly compounded 2x leveraged performance of the S&P High Yield Dividend Aristocrats® Index. 
 The index is designed the measure the performance of the 60 highest dividend yielding S&P Composite 1500 Index constituents, which have followed a managed-dividends policy of consistently increasing dividends every year for at least 25 consecutive years.
